data.text:
Dividing the Night. Lightning from an offshore storm for an instant drives back the night and illuminates the shores of Matanza Beach.
#lightningphotos #floridacoast
#globefocus #lonelyplanet #nikon750 #travel… https://t.co/eowBbrxhee

Storm coming in I wanted to get the drone up before it started raining. Unfortunately,  as I was going up it started, so I couldn't get high. . Cool cloud shot though. @ Saint Augustine Beach, Florida https://t.co/mrioO21yX3

Hey, @jonbellion, your St. Augustine concert was my daughter's Christmas present. We drove from the upstate of SC to see u. It was awesome until the "storm"! The heartbreak was too much, so I'm taking her to Nashville. I could only get lawn tix. Hope we can see u from there!!

Getting my boogie on before the storm rolled in on Vilano last week! 🌊🤙🏼#904 #staug #saintaugustine #vilano #vilanobeach #onlyinduval #fl #florida #beach #ocean #eastcoast #beard #beardgang #boogieboard… https://t.co/ZUrCdseSfF

My work wouldn’t let me off early so I got off the same exact time @jonbellion got on stage and I was 45 mins away from the venue.. Sped my way to the venue under a hard thunder storm and I MADE IT!!! I made it to ONE FUCKING SONG and I’m totally okay with it. I almost cried.. https://t.co/qT7ZXFyQTj

Glorious lightning storm over the island tonight. 

All the clouds are adding to the beauty + lighting up the sky

#staug #staugustine #AnastasiaIsland

At 8:10 PM EDT, 2 S Crescent Beach [St. Johns Co, FL] TRAINED SPOTTER reports HAIL of penny size (E0.75 INCH). A STORM SPOTTER REPORTED NEAR DIME SIZED HAIL FROM STATE ROAD 206 SOUTH TO MATANZAS INLET. https://t.co/VhPb4kdxDg

Shot this earlier today on #Vilano, right before the #storm came in. 🌊🌩 #waveoftheday #904 #staug #staugustine #fl #florida #floridalife #lovefl #igers_staugustine #onlyinduval #vilano #vilanobeach #beach #ocean… https://t.co/7B6Z1LGOHK

That’s it for today. I did a lot of yard work this morning before a pretty decent storm rolled in and I’ve been a bit tired ever since. Time to relax for the evening but I’ll pick back up on this tomorrow. Thanks… https://t.co/cI0uRFRgsb
